DESCRIPTION:Category: Climbing\nLearn how to use flagging to stay balanced and generate power\, engage body tension at the right moments\, and execute deadpoints\, a dynamic movement technique that helps you extend your reach with control. Through focused drills and direct coaching\, you'll develop a stronger awareness of your center of gravity.\nhttps://portal.movementgyms.com/portland/programs/intermediate-technique-flags-and-deadpoints?course=U2Vzc2lvbjoxMDA1MjU2NzM=&date=2026-06-03
